## Project Comments List [/projects/{project_id}/comments/{?per_page,page,project_id,on,id,by}]

### List All Project Comments [GET]

Fetches all available Project Comments with pagination
+ per_page: 15 (number, optional) - The number of results per page.
    + Default: `15`
+ page: 1 (number, optional) - The current page number of results.
    + Default: `1`
+ project_id (number, required)
+ on (string, optional)
+ id (number, optional)
+ by (string, optional )

